<h4>Anatomy of a Good Assessment</h4>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Direct assessments should be as granular as possible</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Tied to a problem on an assignment or quiz</li>
      <li>Overall course grade not fine-grained enough</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Assessments should tie to required subjects</li>
  <li>Assessments should have a target percentage of students who "pass" the assessment</li>
  <li>Each semester or year, actual percentage is gathered</li>
</ul>

