<h2>On the Website</h2>

<p>To create or edit assessments, visit the <strong>"Manage Assessments"</strong> tab.</p>

<%= image_tag "documentation/manage_assessments_tab.png" %>

<h4>Creating Assessments</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Click the <strong>"Manage Assessments"</strong> tab</li>
  <li>Click the <strong>"Create New Asssessment"</strong> button</li>
  <li>
    If you're creating a direct assessment for a subject choose <strong>"by Subject"</strong>. If
    you're trying to create an indirect assessment, choose <strong>"by Course"</strong>.
  </li>
</ul>

<h4>Editing or Archiving Assessments</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Click the <strong>"Manage Assessments"</strong> tab</li>
  <li>Click the <strong>"View Asssessments"</strong> action for course</li>
  <li>Find the assessment and click the action ("Edit", "View", or "Archive")</li>
</ul>
